      "content": "For a universally sophisticated look, the gold standard leans toward classic, understated elegance rather than trendy flashiness. Men should aim for impeccably tailored suits in neutral tones like navy or charcoal, paired with high-quality leather shoes and a conservative tie. For women, tailored separates or classic sheath dresses in muted colors convey authority, complemented by minimal, high-quality jewelry and polished grooming. The key is that everything should look expensive, even if it isn't, suggesting meticulous attention to detail.",
